<apex:page controller="HipaaAuthorizationController" renderAs="pdf" applyHtmlTag="false" applyBodyTag="false" showHeader="false" standardStylesheets="false">
<html>
<head>
<style type="text/css">
    @page {
        size: letter;
        margin: 1in;
        @bottom-center { content: "Page " counter(page) " of " counter(pages); font-size: 9px; color: #666; }
    }
    body { font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 11.5pt; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.5; }
    .firm-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .firm-header .firm-name { font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    .doc-title { text-align: center; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline; margin: 16px 0 20px 0; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .section-title { font-weight: bold; margin: 16px 0 6px 0; font-size: 11.5pt; }
    p { margin: 0 0 10px 0; text-align: justify; }
    table.info-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    table.info-table td { border: 1px solid #999; padding: 5px 8px; vertical-align: top; }
    table.info-table td.label { font-weight: bold; width: 35%; background-color: #f3f3f3; }
    .sig-block { margin-top: 38px; }
    .sig-line { border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a; width: 320px; margin-top: 34px; padding-top: 4px; }
    .sig-caption { font-size: 10pt; color: #444; }
    .date-line { width: 200px; }
    ul { margin: 0 0 10px 18px; padding: 0; }
    li { margin-bottom: 4px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="firm-header">
        <div class="firm-name">{!packet.firmName}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-title">Authorization for Release of Protected Health Information<br/>(HIPAA Authorization)</div>

    <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
            <td class="label">Patient / Client Name</td>
            <td>{!packet.clientFullName}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="label">Date of Birth</td>
            <td>{!dobFormatted}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="label">Intake / Matter #</td>
            <td>{!packet.intakeNumber}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="label">Address</td>
            <td>{!packet.clientAddressLine}, {!packet.clientCity}, {!packet.clientState} {!packet.clientPostalCode}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <p>
        I, the undersigned, hereby authorize any physician, hospital, clinic, pharmacy,
        insurance carrier, employer, or other healthcare or record-holding entity that has
        provided treatment, care, or services to me to release and disclose any and all
        medical records, billing records, and other protected health information ("PHI")
        relating to my care — including but not limited to records concerning the incident
        that occurred on or about <b>{!incidentDateFormatted}</b> — to:
    </p>

    <p style="margin-left:18px;"><b>{!packet.firmName}</b><br/>Attn: {!packet.attorneyName}, Esq.</p>

    <div class="section-title">Purpose of Disclosure</div>
    <p>
        This information is being requested solely in connection with the evaluation,
        investigation, and prosecution of a personal injury claim on my behalf arising
        from the above-referenced incident.
    </p>

    <div class="section-title">Information Authorized for Release</div>
    <ul>
        <li>Complete medical records, including history, examination notes, diagnoses, and treatment plans</li>
        <li>Billing and itemized statement records</li>
        <li>Diagnostic imaging, laboratory, and test results</li>
        <li>Prescription and pharmacy records</li>
        <li>Any other records relevant to the injuries sustained in the above incident</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="section-title">Right to Revoke</div>
    <p>
        I understand that I have the right to revoke this authorization in writing at any
        time, except to the extent that action has already been taken in reliance on it.
        I understand that a revocation must be submitted in writing to the firm listed
        above.
    </p>

    <div class="section-title">Expiration</div>
    <p>
        Unless otherwise revoked, this authorization shall remain in effect for one (1)
        year from the date of signature below, or until the conclusion of the
        above-referenced claim, whichever occurs later.
    </p>

    <p>
        I understand that information disclosed pursuant to this authorization may be
        subject to re-disclosure and may no longer be protected by federal privacy
        regulations once received by the firm named above. A photocopy or electronic copy
        of this authorization shall be considered as valid as the original.
    </p>

    <div class="sig-block">
        <div class="sig-line"></div>
        <div class="sig-caption">Signature of Patient / Client or Authorized Representative</div>
    </div>

    <div class="sig-block">
        <div class="sig-line date-line"></div>
        <div class="sig-caption">Date Signed</div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
</apex:page>